      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  RegularUnit
      RegularUnit contains NOT weighable items.
      class  UnitImplementation
      UnitImplementation contains an item and implements rules for unit price calculation.
      class  WeighableUnit
      WeighableUnit is item that has weight
      Methods in Store that return Unit 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Unit UnitFactory.createUnit(Item item)
      Creates WeighableUnit with 0 weight if item is weighable; If item is not weighable, creates RegularUnit with 0 amount of items.

      Creates WeighableUnit
      Unit UnitFactory.createUnit(Item item, int amount)
      Creates RegularUnit
